eed the Chandrasekhar mass. So KPD\n1930+2752 qualifies as an excellent double degenerate supernova Ia progenitor\ncandidate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2006 13:06:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
